description: Takamaki Ann is a second year student at Shuujin Academy, and is Amamiya Ren`s classmate, and works part-time as a fashion model. Despite being beautiful and kind, before meeting Ren and Ryuuji she has few friends at school, the only one being the volleyball player Suzui Shiho. She later becomes one of the Phantom Thieves with Ren, Ryuuji, and Morgana when she resolves to punish Kamoshida for what he had done to Shiho.
name: Takamaki An
